Seminario_C

Prueba inicial de las tablas de biodiversidad en un notebook

Primero, instalar los paquetes

install.packages(tidyverse)
install.packages(rgbif)

Importamos los paquetes

library(tidyverse)
library(rgbif)
tablita <- occ_data(
  country = "ES",
  year = 2008
)
tablita
Records found [905894] 
Records returned [500] 
Args [occurrenceStatus=PRESENT, limit=500, offset=0, year=2008, country=ES]

Utilizamos rgbif para coger los datos

tabla_completa <- data.frame() 
for (a in 2000:2020){
  for (m in 1:12){
    aux <- occ_data(
      country = "ES",
      year = a,
      month = m,
      limit = 200000
    )
    tabla_res <- aux$data %>%
      select(key, year, month, stateProvince, locality, county, kingdom, species, individualCount)
    tabla_completa <- rbind(tabla_completa, tabla_res)
  }
}
